Release 2.0
===========
* Dark versions of the theme is now released as own plugins Arc Theme Dark and Arc Theme Darker.
* Adjusted dark version editor/table/tree/list/buttons background color to match GTK theme.

Release 1.8
===========
* Added "Arc Dark" theme with blue and orange accented colors.
* Added light and dark editor color schemes. Light matches IntelliJ Light and Dark overrides
  Darcula with many custom color, since originally it was too dark for the panel/editor and text
  was not clearly visible.
* Unified hover effect on buttons and tabs to be lighter and borders on button
  to better match real Arc theme.
* Unified tabs styling, have only hover effect, keep panel color on selected tab (except editor tabs).

Release 1.7
===========
* Use default panel background also for Toolbar.

Release 1.6
===========
* Use default row height in trees.

Release 1.5
===========
* Fixed invisible menu separators for light themes.
* Fixed ScrollBar default background.
* Fixed Notification more button background.

Release 1.4
===========
* Use arc-theme light with blue accent as the default after plugin installation.
* Use white background as default fixes issues with some input boxes using panel background.
* Use same style for DefaultTabs as EditorTabs and TabbedPane.
* Fixed row height in Tree to match Intellij IDEA 2019.2 version.
* Use panel color for ToolTip color.
* Fixed CompletionPopup matched and selected color overlap.
* Unified toolbar separator color to darker.

Release 1.3
===========
* Use white background in plugins UI
* Use accented color for install/update buttons in plugins UI
* Use same height of plugins UI tabs underline
* Fixed visibility of counter (eg. number of plugin updates)

Release 1.2
===========
* Update for IntelliJ 2019.2
* Use accented color for tabs underline
* Added Arc Darker theme with dark menus (its not quite right yet)

Release 1.1
===========
* Set compatibility to all IntelliJ IDEs
* Changed plugin id

Release 1.0
===========
* Initial version of theme.
* Arc light look-alike grey/white colors.
* Accented color is blue (default) or orange.
* Compatible with Intellij IDEA 2019.1+
